      "title": "Documentation of Eden: Wetwork Overlap Kim(?) Riga, Latvia May 29 – July 11, 2026",
      "link": "https://cammisabuerhaus.substack.com/p/test-post",
      "pubDate": "Mon, 13 Jul 2026 16:53:19 GMT",
      "description": "Photography, flatwork, collage, and film.",
      "content": "<h2>Documentation of <em>Eden: Wetwork Overlap</em></h2><p><strong>Kim(?)</strong><br>Riga, Latvia<br>May 29 &#8211; July 11, 2026</p><p>Curator: Zane Onckule<br><br>Documentation of my work presented in <em>Eden: Wetwork Overlap</em></p><p>Insert curatorial text here:</p><p>EDEN: Wet Work Over Lap stages desire as labor and sex as one of its most regulated, exhausted, and persistently unfinished forms. The title, EDEN: Wet Work Over Lap, draws on the double meaning of &#8220;wet work,&#8221; referring both to covert operations and to forms of labor that leave a trace. It is these practices and artworks which expand sexual, emotional, and domestic work into modes of maintenance that accumulate, rather than resolve, into meaning. &#8220;Over Lap&#8221; signals repetition and spill, where actions do not conclude but instead extend across time, overlapping, leaking, and returning.</p><p>With new and existing art works, installations, and performances spanning from analogue processes to &#8220;digital wetwares&#8221;, EDEN: Wet Work Over Lap sustains the infrastructure of desire through exhibition areas associatively shifting between functional sites: bedroom-after hour zone into auditorium, bathroom-wet room into confessional, gym into club into darkroom - all towards a central hall (&#8220;aktu z&#257;le&#8221;), carrying the double meaning of &#8220;akts&#8221;, act and nude, finally climaxing in an exhibitionary attempt to center the concept of exposure as both a performance and condition at once.</p><p>N.B.Festival contains erotic and sexual themes. The exhibition is not recommended for visitors under 18, and minors may enter only with an adult!</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!o9WI!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg\" width=\"1456\" height=\"2183\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/59f66614-a537-4b18-9325-ee6abee93c31_1534x2300.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:2183,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1736825,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://cammisabuerhaus.substack.com/i/206881144?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fim